<pb facs="1079389" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Celeberrimo ac doctissimo Viro 
             <lb/>Petro Antonio <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotto</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><choice><abbr>Joh:</abbr><expan>Johannes</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoulli</rs></salute></opener>
<p><rs key="B_1723-04-16_991170515108505501" type="letter">Litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli vom 16. April 1723</note> 16 <choice><abbr>Apr.</abbr><expan>Aprili</expan></choice> dat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad me rectissime pervenerunt,
         <lb/>ex quibus valetudinem Tuam secundam su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <choice><sic>gau-</sic><corr>gaudio</corr></choice>
<lb/>percepi. Filius meus <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Daniel</rs> nunc <rs key="place_GEO-2661552" type="place">Bern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> agit apud
         <lb/>Fratrem suum <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Nicolaum</rs>, ubi Litteras<rs key="brieftag" type="letter"/> expectavit
         <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs>: in eo vero est ut propedi<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> se itineri co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ittat
         <lb/>ad Vos migraturus, id quod fiet, credo, proximo die
         <lb/>Lun<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>; Fortassis ipsemet has Litteras, quippe quas
         <lb/>ad ipsum mitto, ad Te deportabit. Rogo, ut commendatum
         <lb/>illum Tibi habeas, tam ratione studii medico-prac<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tici, quam ratione valetudinis conservand<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>;
         <lb/>habet enim, ut vide<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">U+F199</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, constitutionem corporis admod<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/>teneram, cui prospici oportet, di<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tam accuratam observando.
         <lb/>Intellexi quidem ex Litteris quibus <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filium</rs> meum honorare
         <lb/>voluisti, <choice><abbr>Clariss.</abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jurinum</rs> ad Te scripsisse at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> significasse
         <lb/>quod animadversiones sit editurus in meam demonstration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
         <lb/>de velocitate aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per foramen vasis effluentis; sed ipsas
         <lb/>has animadversiones videndi certe non magno teneor desi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>derio; quia novi Anglorum genium, qui non tam ex
         <lb/>veritatis amore quam ex <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>mulatione contra perigrinos
         <lb/>scribunt, putantes se solos sapere, sibi omnia deberi, nihil aliis.
         <lb/>Difficultas quam habes in explicatione data per <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filium</rs>
<lb/>meum de cylindro aqueo ex vase effluente, originem
         <lb/>habet tantam ex eo quod mentem ejus non recte
         <pb facs="1079390" n="2"/>
<lb/>assecutus es: Tibi Fraudi fuit terminus quo usus est <hi rend="u">con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>fluere</hi> per quem credidisti quod innuere velit guttulas data
         <lb/>cum velocitate <choice><orig><g ref="#per">U+E670</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> foramen explosas et a se invicem sepa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ratas, postea confluere et ad se mutuo accedere; quod
         <lb/>si res ita intelligenda esset, fateor cylindrum aque<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>um fore breviorem, quam nostra demonstratio exigit:
         <lb/>Sed oportet, ut scias, dicendum potius fuisse guttulas
         <lb/><hi rend="u">diffluere</hi> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <hi rend="u">confluere</hi>, ita nempe ut unaqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
         <lb/>ex guttulis ab utro<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> extremo suo latere <choice><orig><g ref="#per">U+E670</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> dimidi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/>elongetur servata interim puncti medii vel centri
         <lb/>gravitatis velocitate, quo fit ut du<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> guttul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>xim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> expulso hiatu intermedio fiant contigu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>,
         <lb/>idque sic in omnibus cum accidat, vides uti<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> cylindrum
         <lb/>aqueum habiturum suam eandem longitudinem quam
         <lb/>eodem tempore haberet si supposita perfecta
         <lb/>aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fluididate guttul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> a se invicem separat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>manerent; sed etiam, vicissim longitudinem illam
         <lb/>fore ob singulari<unclear>u</unclear>m guttularum diffluxum duplo
         <lb/>graciliorem; id quod cum experientia satis bene conspirat. <!-- figurtag -->
<lb/>Concipe tres istiusmodi guttulas a se invicem
         <lb/>separatas <hi rend="u"><formula>ab</formula></hi>, <hi rend="u"><formula>cd</formula></hi>, <hi rend="u"><formula>ef</formula></hi>, cum interstitiis <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice>
         <lb/><hi rend="u"><formula>bc</formula></hi>, <hi rend="u"><formula>de</formula></hi>, habere datam velocitatem, qua cum tria
         <lb/>centra <hi rend="u"><formula>m</formula></hi>, <hi rend="u"><formula>n</formula></hi>, <hi rend="u"><formula>o</formula></hi>, dato tempore datam longitudi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nem percurrant; concipe nunc eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> quamlibet
         <lb/>guttulam inter movendum diffluere antrorsum et retrors<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualiter, ita ut ex. gr. guttula <hi rend="u"><formula>cd</formula></hi> repleat dimidium
         <lb/>hiatum <hi rend="u"><formula>bc</formula></hi> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tergo et dimidium hiatum <hi rend="u"><formula>de</formula></hi> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> fronte, dum
         <lb/>reliqui dimidii hiatus replen<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">U+F199</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> guttulis <hi rend="u"><formula>ab</formula></hi>, et <hi rend="u"><formula>ef</formula></hi>; ipsa
         <lb/>vero centra <hi rend="u"><formula>m</formula></hi>, <hi rend="u"><formula>n</formula></hi>, <hi rend="u"><formula>o</formula></hi>, pergant invariata velocitate moveri
         <pb facs="1079391" n="3"/>
<lb/>qua ratione intelligi<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">U+F199</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> guttulas etiamsi in unum con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tinuum filum coalescentes nihil tamen de motu suo amit<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tere, nullo existente alio discrimine, quam quod filum
         <lb/><hi rend="u"><formula>ad</formula></hi> sit duplo gracilius quam filum <hi rend="u"><formula>af</formula></hi>, longitudine
         <lb/>interim <hi rend="u"><formula>[m]o</formula></hi><note type="editorial">m undeutlich zu lesen, weil korrigiert. Wirklich m gemeint?</note>, <formula>mo</formula>, manente utrobi<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quali. At<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> sic
         <lb/>puto difficultati Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> satisfactum esse: Spero
         <lb/>autem <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filium</rs> meum h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c Tibi coram latius explica<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>turum; meren<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">U+F199</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> certe nonnullam attention<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, hinc quip<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>pe vide<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">U+F199</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> patescere genuinam rationem physicam, cur filum aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#per">U+E670</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> foramen lamin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ex vase effluentis <choice><sic>gratilescat</sic><corr>gracilescat</corr></choice> in
         <lb/>Diametrum minorem quam est Diameter ipsius
         <lb/>foraminis: Nec video quomodo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jurinus</rs> aut alius ex
         <lb/>Newtonianis hoc Ph<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>nomenum <choice><orig><g ref="#per">U+E670</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> principia sua co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>de explicare queat.</p> <closer><salute>Vale Vir <choice><abbr>clariss.</abbr><expan>clarissime</expan></choice> et me quod facis
            <lb/>amare perge.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>a. d</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1723-05-01">1. Mayi 1723</date></dateline><note type="editorial">Unterstreichung oder Schlussstrich?</note></closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>